http::ext_list::find

Find a token in the list.

Synopsis 
template<
    class T>
const_iterator
find(
    T const& s);
Description
Parameters

Name

Description

s

The token to find. A case-insensitive comparison is used.

Return Value

An iterator to the matching token, or end() if no token exists.
